thread.title: ‘Black Panther’ Again Tops Box Office

author: wsjcom
title: ‘Black Panther’ Again Tops Box Office

organizations.name: again tops box office los angeles

text:
LOS ANGELES—Wakanda’s reign shows no signs of waning. “Black Panther” is king of the box office for the third straight weekend.
The release from Marvel and Disney brought in $65.7 million domestically over the weekend, easily outpacing new releases “Red Sparrow” and “Death Wish,” according to studio estimates Sunday.
